{"tid":1300601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實藍底嘅唔會睇你地所謂文宣嘅野","createTime":"2019-07-09T11:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T12:19:56.000Z","uid":218575,"like":59,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e66bd3747bce7796da067530a738333af2b6d908","tid":1300601,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:56:29.000Z","msg":"佢地只會揀自己啱睇嘅野黎睇<br />\n就好似你地都唔會睇港人講地嘅野咁 <br />\n我頭先特登去咗睇何志光youtube 嘅政治揭露<br />\n同陳怡最新條片 <br />\n<br />\n先唔論政治立場<br />\n何志光俾我感覺就係癡線佬<br />\n連登仔就一味話癡線佬唔洗理佢啦<br />\n但大把藍底嘅人當正佢講嘅野真理咁<br />\n有睇高佢啲片嘅就知佢大把歪理<br />\n日日搭地鐵成班廢中廢老係到睇佢啲片<br />\n我睇唔夠3分鐘直接檢舉<br />\n<br />\n反而撐警/送中嘅店舖大把人狙擊<br />\n呢啲直接歪理當真理洗人腦嘅youtube channel<br />\n就完全無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔明點解連登無人理呢兩條友嘅片<br />\n佢地個channel 仲可以生存到咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ffcc32cdb068a23db8a34639011c3de91e783df","tid":1300601,"uid":218575,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:58:25.000Z","msg":"某程度上呢啲咁嘅洗腦youtube channel<br />\n仲恐撚怖語撐警/送中嘅舖頭<br />\n佢地直情就係藍絲嘅文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但完全無連登仔去理"},{"pid":"5328d8c164440c9e34237dfea648618ffd820f15","tid":1300601,"uid":431,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:59:57.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />send完佢哋直接skip<br />\n好撚嬲"},{"pid":"10eff6bad119675443956537dd02fd34082ba2f4","tid":1300601,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"【九大訴求】陳同佳案，醫管局 唔可以不了了之<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1300409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1300409</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d934358be17b0137cf5d8795b27e2a8752a6034","tid":1300601,"uid":218575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5328d8c164440c9e34237dfea648618ffd820f15","tid":1300601,"uid":431,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"